Rixos Hotel in Dubai at Palm Jumeirah is currently looking for a Waitress preferably Russian speaker to join their dynamic and energetic team.
At least 1 to 2 years experienced in the same position in a 5 Star Hotel. Must be  currently in UAE.
Rixos The Palm, Dubai
Rixos The Palm, Dubai is a selective resort combining Leisure, Business and Holiday destination by offering meeting venues, family entertainment activities and Business services.
